In this podcast, Professor Christopher Yoo of 1 World Connected interviews Michael Spencer from Smart Money International. SmartMoney is a Uganda-based financial services and education company that promotes savings by providing rural African communities with a mobile-based savings and payment service that is safer, cheaper, and more convenient than conventional mobile money, banks, and cash.

The full podcast can be listened to on [SoundCloud at this link](https://soundcloud.com/user-658188477/smartmoney)
